episodes.title: The Blackburn Death Cult...in Los Angeles   4K
episodes.description:
You heard about Charles Manson and The Manson Family.  You heard about Jim Jones and The People's Temple...join us as we track down The Blackburn Cult in Los Angeles, California.  The Blackburn Cult, officially called The Divine Order of the Royal Arms of the Great Eleven, or the Great Eleven Club, was a religious movement started in 1922 by May Otis Blackburn and her daughter Ruth.  Things took a turn for the worst when murder, theft, faith healing and trying to resurrect the dead came into the mix.

This is their story...
